response.original_title: Eddie Bravo Invitational 18: The Female Strawweights
response.overview: This Sunday, December 9, 2018, the Eddie Bravo Invitational invades the Onnit Gym in Austin, Texas for EBI 18 featuring a 16-woman strawweight tournament starting at 8 p.m. ET and 5 p.m. PT.
